Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點 夏露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快叫醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.18,0:01:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那件事進行的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 一切都還算順利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差那最後的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.99,0:01:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一步先別使出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南非那邊的企業
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也收購得很成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也又再邁進一步了
;Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.51,0:01:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.71,0:01:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來有計劃安排出國的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點神經衰弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先給她好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露 身體不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她關在房裡做什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總有一天會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說收購汽車公司只是個幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上\N是想要南非大葉工業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是葛蘿莉亞家的生產線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露也受了相當的打擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣讓夏露做下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 夏露怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗可不用知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好找個能做夏露工作的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來支撐這個家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 你沒這種才能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 是誰能做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我之外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那二人的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知他們做得來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他們有這個才能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘量別引起騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說你做不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她似乎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很期望你和綺羅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和綺羅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和葛蘿莉亞家有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你當我們家的一家之主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也願意做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被看見的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一個人靜一靜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是很有威嚴的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是說你是這家之主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不正確的囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面上是我支持這個家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那都是夏露的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也做不來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你…打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我必須向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有隱藏的事未說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 你和蓋魯克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是葛蘿莉亞家的\N指定繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你們和我們結合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們世代都會流有你的血統
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才跟我說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不想強迫你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你能夠很自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會想起這個家時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有葛蘿莉亞的血統
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姆里克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姆里克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體覺得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姆里克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姆里克斯把你看做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他的母親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會離開你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很喜歡你的味道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看 別摸 別接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電腦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:08:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別隨便亂摸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先交給我來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像我也流著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你們一樣的血統
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣的血統
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 一樣的血統
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 接下來的問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南非鑽石工廠的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個工廠被一家大企業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從中偷買股權\N要將其奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而政府也以緊急事件處理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然鑽石產量減少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收入也將減半
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是瑪麗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先減薪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再向當地政府
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始先這樣摸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想吃吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就像冰淇淋一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美她說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師一定會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我來做就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗我不行做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是一直都是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道雪希兒的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把老師佔為己有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡只有瑪麗是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗的雙親早亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後吃了不少苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自己什麼也不說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她來到葛蘿莉亞家後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去碰難過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能一直把她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關在溫室裡面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗她自己也想出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫室裡起了大風
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許那就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家的當家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒這興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是當的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有上億的財產
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落入口袋裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要財產呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是要女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要當這家之主的路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎比你快了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅好像也發覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一臉不在乎的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有份 我也有份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是最好的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真認真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有時也會誇獎人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希兒說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師很怕雷電
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我來陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真溫柔體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師下面的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做 會不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮 瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗好怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像自己不是自己的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗要改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 卻覺得很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要到那去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就會改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑽石工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識南非當地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位很厲害的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去麻煩他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有幫助的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是個好辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說瑪麗很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都願意幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家卻說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗可以不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是南非的大總統
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…你說舞會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你來拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在對葛蘿莉亞家而言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多重要的時期
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜雪兒夫人 瑪麗她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了葛蘿莉亞家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做我做得到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是夏露的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你能讓瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照他的想法去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再什麼也幫不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師也會在身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和老師在一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布敏先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正等您來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 是瑪麗說要辦宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個人的主意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在打什麼主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜雪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜雪兒妳在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳邀我來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼悠閒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說礦場那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快被收購走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天邀請各位來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗葛蘿莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是南非的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他們會在這
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天從南非而來的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也到了現場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可伏克總統
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀請我到這來

